{
  "stem": "4226.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We just ignored them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You feel that you want to survive, but you didn't care if-- practically the only time we, we had a-- we were off work in the time of the alarm.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just sitting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, we, we, we know this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they, they dropped silver papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some-- after the raid gone, the silver papers still keep coming for 120 minutes, 130 minutes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Those which opened up, they were flickering in the air.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But some didn't open, the bundle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The whole bundle came down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some German guys took it for decorating their future Christmas tree in December,",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they dropped them to, to confuse their other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're measuring--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--up their attitude, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we, we knew roughly where, where the thing, whatever, fights on the Rhine and, and Holland border.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "More or less.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We know were the Russians were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I had these two German papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of them, the news which you read in it was two, two, three weeks old.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you add another hundred meter for the Russians to the west, another hundred kilometers to the Americans to the east.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And more or less-- [LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Allach, that was a-- I recall that was still in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we arrived in Allach, were still warm days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And did I mention this to you before?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Friday night, they call it [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's weekend.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We came home from work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We don't go out to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Saturday, we work half a day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Saturday afternoons and Sunday, we were off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We came in Friday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had Appell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they-- the kapo, he was a very cruel German kapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His name was Knoll-- K-N-O double L, Knoll.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He, he--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His surname, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
